{"tid":1132643,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"[不安]斜對面屋個阿婆成日開門裝我","createTime":"2019-04-30T12:39:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-02T12:30:55.000Z","uid":22560,"like":21,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"b0bd5cfd8ebaa1339be9282aa7fe421d4664a6d1","tid":1132643,"uid":22560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T12:39:00.000Z","msg":"話說我斜對面屋就一直住咗個阿婆<br />\n我有時返屋企或者出門口嗰陣<br />\n個阿婆一聽到聲，就會專登極快速咁開門伸個頭出嚟裝我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一直望實我，直至到我入咗屋或者走咗為止<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我試過同佢鬥望，但每次我都係輸，實在太不安<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有冇人諗到佢到底咩事<br />\n係咩心態<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3ad2d904415cd1f564a745d228fb0c198ec890e","tid":1132643,"uid":225760,"like":25,"dislike":0,"score":25,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T12:40:17.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8d93d01db97d1ba43e4708490778f4753c9b0dd2","tid":1132643,"uid":196484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T12:41:45.000Z","msg":"你試下細細聲偷偷哋出門口"},{"pid":"1b2ed007c4452b89056acd22d72d74da7d6e8018","tid":1132643,"uid":194824,"like":21,"dislike":3,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T12:44:53.000Z","msg":"你男定女先<br />\n<br />\n男嘅咪想吸精返陽<br />\n女嘅咪想安插鬼胎"},{"pid":"145108756601783650baa1d51b99a3bbe5130705","tid":1132643,"uid":181581,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T14:14:35.000Z","msg":"佢想同你扑野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e11966cee4185f1e32023b71273c214047e2d62","tid":1132643,"uid":4363,"like":2,"dislike":9,"score":-7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T14:17:55.000Z","msg":"呀婆都未屌你次撚次想開門透透氣<br />\n你條撚屌都咁岩做兩秒返黎<br />\n每次諗住兇到你 做少少/遲少少返<br />\n廢事咁撚尷尬<br />\n點知dllm你次次都望返佢"},{"pid":"f9025b78a741badf4ffe0e89958f76942b6aa0be","tid":1132643,"uid":17628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T14:19:30.000Z","msg":"你問佢囉"},{"pid":"a21b59672378812c58a0b7773c1c2611d7b480d1","tid":1132643,"uid":229767,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T14:22:38.000Z","msg":"阿婆冇人探而你個樣似佢屋企人"},{"pid":"15cb3b832ecc5240eb1db72e60015c2058e17d3c","tid":1132643,"uid":243854,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T14:25:40.000Z","msg":"係咪獨居老人覺得悶呀<br />\n以前我隔離有個呀婆自己住，成日都拎啲橙呀鮑魚麵畀我食，睇得出佢真係幾悶"},{"pid":"3337723e0b5cc0b2be2e942d33d9af73c9e5435f","tid":1132643,"uid":22560,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"15cb3b832ecc5240eb1db72e60015c2058e17d3c","tid":1132643,"uid":243854,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T14:25:40.000Z","msg":"係咪獨居老人覺得悶呀<br />\n以前我隔離有個呀婆自己住，成日都拎啲橙呀鮑魚麵畀我食，睇得出佢真係幾悶"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-01T02:28:40.000Z","msg":"但佢咁樣眼都唔眨咁望實我真係好驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3af7c0c55083387b5b5bd9a387071038cbb83e82","tid":1132643,"uid":108359,"like":15,"dislike":1,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-01T02:30:53.000Z","msg":"隔離鄰舍 咪講聲婆婆早晨 係咪有野要幫手"},{"pid":"599af0cf27cfee77b96b8f7014af143e44e60020","tid":1132643,"uid":181997,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"3337723e0b5cc0b2be2e942d33d9af73c9e5435f","tid":1132643,"uid":22560,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"15cb3b832ecc5240eb1db72e60015c2058e17d3c","tid":1132643,"uid":243854,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T14:25:40.000Z","msg":"係咪獨居老人覺得悶呀<br />\n以前我隔離有個呀婆自己住，成日都拎啲橙呀鮑魚麵畀我食，睇得出佢真係幾悶"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-01T02:28:40.000Z","msg":"但佢咁樣眼都唔眨咁望實我真係好驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-01T02:32:17.000Z","msg":"咁你咪望住佢係咁眨眼囉"},{"pid":"6dd2e7a81bce44b1664f40690